HEADWORD: Insufferably
<hw>In*suf"fer*a*bly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a manner or to a
degree beyond endurance; intolerably; <as>as, a blaze
<ex>insufferably</ex> bright; a person <ex>insufferably</ex>
proud.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

